OL,6,
OL,7,GOfcom is expected to say soon whether
OL,8,Git will run a full consultation on
OL,9,Gchanges to the TV advertising rules.
OL,11,
OL,12,FIt sought views over the summer on
OL,13,Fwhether there was a case to change the
OL,14,Fextra rules covering ITV, Channel 4 and
OL,15,FChannel 5.
OL,17,
OL,18,FThe three PSBs have less advertising in
OL,19,Ftotal than other commercial channels
OL,20,Fand rules on the frequency of breaks
OL,21,Fare tighter.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,22,                                   G1/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
