OL,6,
OL,7,FBut if you've been watching I'm a
OL,8,FCelebrity, you'll be aware of the kind
OL,9,Fof archaic compromises ITV has to make
OL,10,Fto stay within the rules.
OL,12,
OL,13,FITV is allowed 40 minutes of
OL,14,Fadvertising between 6pm and 11pm with
OL,15,Fno more than 12 minutes in each hour.
OL,17,
OL,18,FOn a typical weeknight, there are 4
OL,19,Fminutes of ads before 7pm with the
OL,20,Fremaining 36 minutes shared out between
OL,21,F7pm and the start of News at Ten.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,22,                                   G2/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
