OL,6,
OL,7,FHowever the channel naturally wants to
OL,8,Fmake the best use of the limited
OL,9,Fadvertising time available.
OL,11,
OL,12,FI'm a Celebrity runs until around
OL,13,F10.30pm some evenings. So advertising
OL,14,Fis taken away from less lucrative slots
OL,15,Fso it can be slotted into the ratings
OL,16,Fjuggernaut.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,22,                                   G3/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
