OL,6,
OL,7,FFor instance, on Monday and Tuesday
OL,8,Flast week, there were no ad breaks
OL,9,Fbetween the start of the regional news
OL,10,Fat 6pm and Emmerdale at 7.30pm.
OL,12,
OL,13,FBut if you imagine there was some
OL,14,Fbenefit to viewers in this, think
OL,15,Fagain.
OL,17,
OL,18,FInstead, the network news followed its
OL,19,Fusual format but the ad breaks were
OL,20,Freplaced by what I call the Trailer
OL,21,FBreaks of Doom.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,22,                                   G4/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
