OL,6,
OL,7,FThese are the full-length breaks
OL,8,Fdesigned for commercials which are
OL,9,Ffilled entirely by promotions because
OL,10,Fof the rules on the volume of
OL,11,Fadvertising on PSBs.
OL,13,
OL,14,FIt is important to look properly at
OL,15,Fwhether there are genuine economic
OL,16,Fbenefits to advertisers and
OL,17,Fbroadcasters from allowing more
OL,18,Fadvertising. It is possible they may
OL,19,Fconclude that the same amount of
OL,20,Fadvertising spending could simply be
OL,21,Fspread more thinly.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,22,                                   G5/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
