OL,6,
OL,7,FIt should also be clear that
OL,8,Fbroadcasters do not need to use their
OL,9,Fwhole allocation if they conclude that
OL,10,F"less is more"  could rationed
OL,11,Fadvertising command a premium or boost
OL,12,Fratings?
OL,14,
OL,15,FBut, as I've argued before, it is hard
OL,16,Fto claim that viewers will lose out if
OL,17,FITV and others have a full 12 minutes
OL,18,Fof ads all through the most popular
OL,19,Fviewing hours.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
